A simple PathPlanning demo

Requirements:
You need the OpenGL Utility Toolkit (GLUT) to compile this demo

usage:
PathPlannerDemo <scene filename>

usage example:
PathPlannerDemo ../../files/MultiRobotDemo/Scene.wu

Instructions:
Use the keys '0' to '9' to select a joint to move
Use the '-' and '+' keys to move the selected joint
Use the 'HOME' key to select qInit (note: qInit must be collision free)
Use the 'END' key to select qGoal (note: qGoal must be collision free)
Use the 'RETURN' key to execute the pathplanner
Use the 's' key to switch to the straightline pathplanner
Use the 'r' key to switch to the RRT pathplanner (default)
Use the 'l' key to switch to the LazyPRM pathplanner
Use the 'd' key to replay the last animation
